  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine ground lamb, garlic, parsley, black pepper, and grated Parmesan cheese.",
    "Stir in shredded cheddar cheese until just combined.",
    "Transfer mixture into an oven-safe baking dish.",
    "Squeeze lemon juice over the top of the filling to add flavor and prevent browning.",
    "Bake for about 20-25 minutes or until heated through. Let sit for a few minutes before serving.",
    "Serve with pita bread or other Syrian-inspired sides if desired."
